{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，明日及星期二仍有幾陣驟雨，早上稍涼，最低氣溫約21、22度。隨後兩三日氣溫逐步回升。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月3日(日)</cell>\n        <cell>5月4日(一)</cell>\n        <cell>5月5日(二)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>21度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>南風3級，後轉北風4級，間中5級。</cell>\n        <cell>北至東北風4至5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4至5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>75-95%</cell>\n        <cell>65-90%</cell>\n        <cell>75-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>高</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上短暫時間有陽光。稍後驟雨增多及有狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，早晚有幾陣驟雨。日間部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月6日(三)</cell>\n        <cell>5月7日(四)</cell>\n        <cell>5月8日(五)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>30度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>東風4級，離岸間中5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東南風4級。</cell>\n        <cell>南至東南風3級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>70-85%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n        <cell>65-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，日間短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有一兩陣驟雨。日間短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光。稍後有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-02T23:27:21.512370+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":489,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}